# Flask and venv 

 Installing flask:
   https://flask.palletsprojects.com/en/2.1.x/installation/

 Creating Virtual Environment:
   https://packaging.python.org/en/latest/tutorials/installing-packages/#creating-and-using-virtual-environments

# Environment variables

(Also see README)

FLASK_APP 		needs to be the name of the main script (config_ui.py)
FLASK_ENV 		should be set to 'development'
UICONFIG_SETTINGS 	variable used by the main script, path to the config file for the app 

# Custom settings

UICONFIG_SETTINGS points to a config file which should have the following variable set:

CONFIG_PATH=[Path to the config file which sits in a local cloned source tree for spb-seqware-production repo]
PRESET_PATH=[Path to a .conf file with presets used to configure the projects]
DEFAULTS_PATH=[Path to a .conf file with pre-filled defaults]


